				Class
			========================
			========================

Class is collection of variables and methods.
where variables hold data and methods perform operations (it may be any of kind operations)
class is defined by class  keyword 
this is blueprint of objects


				Syntax of Class
			=============================
			

class ClassName:
	-----------------------------  Statement 1
	-----------------------------  Statement 2	
	-----------------------------  Statement 3
	-----------------------------  Statement 4


Ex-

Class Company:

	"This Company Name is XYZ , This is Located in Banglore"
	
	def  Details(self):

		print("This is IT Company")


-------------------------------
------------------------------
>>>c=Company( )		

>>>c.Details( )		#This is IT Company

>>>c.__doc__		#This Company Name is XYZ ,This is Located in Banglore



