E). How to delete Static Variable of a Class
==================================
=======================================Syntax======================================

del  ClassName.VariableName


Ex--
====
====

>>> class Test:
	a=10
	@classmethod
	def m1(cls):
		del cls.a

		
>>> Test.m1( )
>>> print(Test.__dict__)
{'__module__': '__main__', 'm1': <classmethod object at 0x000001F986C9F7F0>, '__dict__': <attribute '__dict__' of 'Test' objects>,
'__weakref__': <attribute '__weakref__' of 'Test' objects>, '__doc__': None}

